{"tid":179083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國醫學研究：男人望大奶 / 可愛動物 有助健康！","createTime":"2017-03-30T04:02:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T09:43:09.000Z","uid":29314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1592184db4a96681ef44e453c30ea729932ed731","tid":179083,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T04:02:47.000Z","msg":"據美國《每日醫學》報導，一份發表在《內科醫學誌》(Archives of Internal Medicine)的研究報告指出，<span style=\"color: red;\">男人盯著大奶看就會有正面思考，進而對健康有所幫助，看可愛動物也會有相同效果</span>。<br />\n<br />\n此外，做愛也對長壽有幫助，因為科學研究顯示，做愛可以降低50%死亡率，如果有更多的高潮，平均可以比一般人多活3~8年。"},{"pid":"4c030f14e88ef827d4f6b4d74b4528eddd636dcf","tid":179083,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T04:11:42.000Z","msg":"你想連登巴打唔健康姐 圖都冇張"},{"pid":"7829df33ea4b80961ebf99e6b4459018ccba64a7","tid":179083,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T04:17:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/54emifn1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F54emifn1&h=3fcf05f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隻貓好得意"},{"pid":"b994ddf6acf90c18a3bc58023f7acb3efac19389","tid":179083,"uid":660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T04:25:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://punchline.asia/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/054627mhziibrymscyscrc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpunchline.asia%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F01%2F054627mhziibrymscyscrc.png&h=bd4aee6f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"99ebf3ac0d2e2ebfffac1a9c1f3cc90911d285a1","tid":179083,"uid":40779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T04:27:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位巴打身體健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57218cec6d1374ba07682284241041d77ff0cd7f","tid":179083,"uid":23021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T04:27:57.000Z","msg":"